Print enspls.od Object

Source: R/print.enspls.R
print.enspls.od.Rd

Print enspls.od object.

# S3 method for enspls.od
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An object of class enspls.od.
...

Additional parameters for print.

See also

See enspls.od for outlier detection with ensemble sparse partial least squares regressions.

Examples

data("logd1k")
x = logd1k$x
y = logd1k$y

set.seed(42)
od = enspls.od(
  x, y, reptimes = 5, maxcomp = 3,
  alpha = c(0.3, 0.6, 0.9))
print(od)
